Author: SalehRobbins
Text: I relate to the first 3. You're not alone. Sometimes the ED guilt goes away and I'm "normal," but I still want to lose weight. Staying with it is hard during these periods because the extreme stress and fear of food goes away.

Author: glokash
Text: I wish I has something more helpful to say. I'm sorry. Life fucking sucks sometimes but that doesn't mean it always will.
